Name: ROM Repair - Only a bit broken
Description: A portion of the ROM is broken and needs to be rewritten. We know some of its inputs and outputs but not much else.
StartingComments:
A portion of the ROM has been corrupted; you'll need to deduce the function and implement it. The function only needs a single word, which gets fed in from TOP.

f(1) = f(2) = f(4) = f(8) = ... = 1
f(3) = f(5) = 2
f(46) = f(673) = 3
f(-1) = 12
Implement it as an infinite loop.
